We take your privacy very seriously. This platform is designed to collect as little data as possible.

## 1. Data Controller

**Company Name**
Address

Email: privacy@example.com

## 2. Use of Cookies and Local-/Session Storage

When visiting this site, a few bits of functional information may be stored on your device:
- If you are not logged in, only information about the current state of the window is stored in your browser. This information is deleted when you close the tab.
- If you are logged in, additional information is permanently stored in your Browser until you log out:
    1. Access- and refresh-tokens for your current session
    2. Information about your user account
    3. Information about whether or not you have dismissed the cookie information banner


## 3. Data Collected

When you create an account on this site, the following data will be collected:

- **Account data**: Username
- **Translation data**: All of the translations you create will be stored permanently.<br>
You can request the removal of your work at any time without a specific reason (please contact me at contact@wehrfritz.me to do so).<br>
Improvement suggestions for existing translations are automatically deleted when you delete your account or when they are either accepted or rejected.

E-mail addresses are not collected or used. For the purpose of account recovery, you will be given a number of secret words.


Regardless of whether you are registered, logged in or not, some personally identifiable information about you and your device (like your public IP address, browser agent and some information about your device may appear in transient logs).

## 4. Purpose of Processing

We process your data to:

- Provide and operate the localization platform
- Ensure security and prevent abuse

**None of the collected data is shared with any third party.**

## 5. Data Retention

Account data is retained for as long as your account is active. You can delete your account at any time from the Settings page.

## 6. Your Rights

Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact me at contact@wehrfritz.me to exercise these rights.
